### Change a users password
PATCH https://{{HOST}}/users/test@test.com
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
	"password": "newpassword"
}


### Delete a user
DELETE https://{{HOST}}/users/test@test.com
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


